<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Microphone Labs üê®</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css"> 
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #141414;
            --surface: #1f1f1f;
            --border: #333;
            --accent: #d05ce3;
        }
        body { 
            overflow-y: auto; 
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: #e0e0e0;
        } 
        
        .app-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
            height: auto;
        }

        /* HEADER & CONTROLS */
        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
        }
        .header-left h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        .controls { 
            display: flex; 
            gap: 8px; 
            align-items: center; 
            flex-wrap: wrap; 
        }
        .controls select, .controls button {
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            background: #2a2a2a;
            color: white;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        .controls button.primary { background: var(--accent); color: black; font-weight: bold; border: none; }
        .controls button.action { background: #333; }
        
        /* GRID LAYOUT */
        .bento-grid { 
            display: grid; 
            grid-template-columns: 22% 1fr 22%;
            grid-template-rows: 1fr;
            gap: 15px; 
            padding: 15px;
            flex-grow: 1;
            overflow: visible; 
        }
        
        .col-left, .col-center, .col-right { 
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            gap: 15px; 
            height: auto; 
            min-width: 0; /* Important for flex/grid children */
            transition: all 0.1s ease;
        }
        
        /* CARDS */
        .card { 
            background: var(--surface); 
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 12px;
            display: flex; 
            flex-direction: column; 
            flex: 1;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            min-height: 0; /* Allow shrinking */
        }
        
        .card h2 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            color: #888;
            display: flex; 
            justify-content: space-between; 
            align-items: center;
        }

        /* Specific Sizing */
        .scope-card { flex: 2; } 
        canvas { 
            flex-grow: 1; 
            width: 100%; 
            height: 100%; 
            background: #000; 
            border-radius: 4px; 
            transition: all 0.1s ease;
        }

        /* RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS */
        @media (max-width: 850px) {
            body { overflow: auto; }
            .app-container { height: auto; max-height: none; }
            .bento-grid { 
                display: flex;
                flex-direction: column;
                height: auto;
                overflow: visible;
            }
            .col-left, .col-center, .col-right { height: auto; }
            
            .scope-card { height: 400px; min-height: 400px; }
            .card { min-height: auto; }
            canvas { min-height: 200px; }
            
            header { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; text-align: center; }
            .controls { justify-content: center; }
            .controls select { flex-grow: 1; }
        }
    </style>
    <style>
        /* 7040 SMART FIT PATCH */
        
        /* 1. SCROLL FALLBACK: Allow scrolling if content is too tall */
        body { overflow-y: auto !important; height: 100vh; }
        .app-container { height: auto !important; min-height: 100vh; }
        
        /* 2. COMPACT LAYOUT: Shrink gaps to fit 1080p screens */
        .bento-grid { 
            gap: 10px !important; 
            padding: 10px !important; 
            /* Subtract header height to calculate ideal fit */
            height: calc(100vh - 60px) !important; 
            min-height: 600px; /* Don't squash too much */
        }

        /* 3. CARD SIZING: Make Scope flexy, Tone fixed */
        .col-left, .col-center, .col-right { gap: 10px !important; }
        .card { padding: 10px !important; }
        
        /* The scope card should shrink to let Tone B fit */
        .scope-card { 
            flex: 1 1 auto !important; /* Grow and Shrink */
            min-height: 250px;         /* Minimum usable height */
        }
        
        /* Tone card shouldn't squash */
        /* Use a broader selector if :has isn't supported everywhere, but it's fine for modern labs */
        .card:has(#tone-vol) { flex: 0 0 auto !important; }

        /* 4. COMPACT CONTROLS: Save vertical space */
        h2 { margin-bottom: 5px !important; font-size: 0.85rem !important; }
        .inline-controls { gap: 5px !important; }
        button, select, input { padding: 4px 8px !important; font-size: 0.85rem !important; }
        
        /* Canvas should fill available space */
        canvas { height: 100% !important; }

        /* MODAL STYLES */
        .modal-overlay { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85); z-index: 1000; display: none; justify-content: center; align-items: center; backdrop-filter: blur(5px); }
        .modal-content { background: #141414; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; width: 90%; max-width: 900px; max-height: 95vh; overflow-y: auto; border: 1px solid #333; display: flex; flex-direction: column; box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
        .modal-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 1px solid #333; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        .btn-close { background: none; border: none; color: #fff; font-size: 2rem; cursor: pointer; line-height: 1; }
        #spectrum-modal-canvas { width: 100%; height: 300px; background: black; border-radius: 4px; flex-shrink: 0; border: 1px solid #333; }
        .modal-body { margin-top: 20px; color: #ccc; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        .modal-body h3 { color: var(--accent); margin-top: 0; }
        .math-block { background: #0a0a0a; padding: 10px; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center; margin: 15px 0; border: 1px solid #222; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 1.2rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="app-container" style="height: 100vh;">
    
    <header>
        <div class="header-left">
            <a href="../index.html" class="home-link">
                <h1>Microphone <span class="highlight">Labs</span> üê®</h1>
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="controls inline-controls">
            <select id="device-select"><option>Detecting...</option></select>
            <button id="btn-start" class="btn primary">Start Mic</button>
            <button id="btn-stop" class="btn action">Stop</button>
            <button id="btn-help" class="btn secondary">Lab Guide</button>
            <span id="mic-status" class="status-badge warn">Idle</span>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="bento-grid">
        <div class="col-left">
            <div class="panel card">
                <h2>Spectrum üìä <button class="btn action" id="btn-copy-spectrum" style="float:right; padding:2px 8px; font-size:0.7rem;">CSV</button></h2>
                <canvas id="spectrum-canvas"></canvas>
                <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; margin-top:5px; color:#aaa; font-size:0.9rem;">
                    <span>RMS: <b id="amp-rms" style="color:var(--accent);">--</b></span>
                    <span>dB: <b id="amp-db">--</b></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel card" style="flex: 0 0 150px;">
                <h2>Pitch üéµ</h2>
                <div style="text-align:center; font-size:2.5rem; color:var(--accent); font-weight:bold; margin-top:10px;" id="freq-fundamental">--</div>
                <div style="text-align:center; color:#666;">Confidence: <span id="freq-confidence">0%</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel card" style="flex: 0 0 160px;">
                <h2>Quick Guide</h2>
                <ul style="margin:0; padding-left:16px; color:#bbb; font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.5;">
                    <li>Choose a mic, press Start.</li>
                    <li>Spectrum: strongest bins = loudest freqs.</li>
                    <li>Pitch: locks on single tones.</li>
                    <li>Scope: zoom/gain for waveform; copy CSV for analysis.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-center">
            <div class="panel card scope-card">
                <h2>Oscilloscope „Ä∞Ô∏è <span id="scope-input-freq" style="color:var(--accent); font-size:0.8rem; margin-left:10px;">Freq: --</span></h2>
                
                <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:10px; align-items:center; background:#000; padding:8px; border-radius:6px; margin-bottom:10px; font-size:0.8rem;">
                    
                    <label style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2px;">
                        <span style="color:#888;">Sec/Div</span>
                        <select id="scope-tdiv" style="width:80px; padding:2px; background:#222; color:white; border:1px solid #444;">
                            <option value="0.00005">50 ¬µs</option>
                            <option value="0.0001">100 ¬µs</option>
                            <option value="0.0002">200 ¬µs</option>
                            <option value="0.0005">500 ¬µs</option>
                            <option value="0.001" selected>1 ms</option>
                            <option value="0.002">2 ms</option>
                            <option value="0.005">5 ms</option>
                        </select>
                    </label>

                    <label style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2px;">
                        <span style="color:#888;">Volts/Div</span>
                        <select id="scope-vdiv" style="width:80px; padding:2px; background:#222; color:white; border:1px solid #444;">
                            <option value="0.1">0.1 V</option>
                            <option value="0.2">0.2 V</option>
                            <option value="0.5">0.5 V</option>
                            <option value="1.0" selected>1 V</option>
                            <option value="2.0">2 V</option>
                            <option value="5.0">5 V</option>
                            <option value="10.0">10 V</option>
                        </select>
                    </label>

                    <label style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2px; flex:1; min-width:80px;">
                        <span style="color:#888;">H-Offset</span>
                        <input type="range" id="scope-h-offset" min="-5" max="5" step="0.1" value="0">
                    </label>
                    <label style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:2px; flex:1; min-width:80px;">
                        <span style="color:#888;">V-Offset</span>
                        <input type="range" id="scope-v-offset" min="-2" max="2" step="0.1" value="0">
                    </label>

                    <button class="btn action" id="btn-scope-pause" style="padding:4px 10px; height:32px;">Pause</button>
                    <button class="btn action" id="btn-rec-export" style="padding:4px 10px; height:32px;">Export</button>
                </div>

                <canvas id="scope-canvas"></canvas>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel card" style="flex: 0 0 auto;">
                <h2>Tone Gen (Superposition) üîä</h2>
                <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:8px;">
                    
                    <div style="display:flex; gap:10px; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
                        <button id="btn-tone-toggle" class="btn action" style="flex:1; padding:8px; min-width:60px;">PLAY</button>
                        <div style="flex:2; min-width:120px;">
                            <label style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; font-size:0.8rem;">Master Vol: <span id="tone-vol-val">50</span>%</label>
                            <input type="range" id="tone-vol" min="0" max="1" step="0.01" value="0.5" style="width:100%">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div style="background:#222; padding:8px; border-radius:6px; border-left: 3px solid var(--accent);">
                        <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:6px; margin-bottom:6px;">
                            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;">
                                <strong style="font-size:0.8rem; color:var(--accent);">Tone A</strong>
                                <select id="tone-type-a" style="padding:2px; font-size:0.75rem; background:#000; color:#fff; border:1px solid #444; border-radius:3px; width:70px;">
                                    <option value="sine">Sine</option>
                                    <option value="square">Square</option>
                                    <option value="sawtooth">Saw</option>
                                    <option value="triangle">Tri</option>
                                    <option value="none">Off</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <span id="tone-freq-a-val" style="font-size:0.8rem; font-family:monospace; min-width:30px; text-align:right;">440 Hz</span>
                        </div>
                        <input type="range" id="tone-freq-a" min="50" max="1000" value="440" style="width:100%; display:block;">
                    </div>

                    <div style="background:#222; padding:8px; border-radius:6px; border-left: 3px solid #4facfe;">
                        <div style="display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:6px; margin-bottom:6px;">
                            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:6px;">
                                <strong style="font-size:0.8rem; color:#4facfe;">Tone B</strong>
                                <select id="tone-type-b" style="padding:2px; font-size:0.75rem; background:#000; color:#fff; border:1px solid #444; border-radius:3px; width:70px;">
                                    <option value="sine">Sine</option>
                                    <option value="square">Square</option>
                                    <option value="sawtooth">Saw</option>
                                    <option value="triangle">Tri</option>
                                    <option value="none">Off</option>
                                </select>
                            </div>
                            <div style="display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;">
                                <label style="font-size:0.7rem; color:#aaa; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:3px; cursor:pointer; background:#333; padding:2px 5px; border-radius:3px;">
                                    <input type="checkbox" id="tone-link" checked> Link
                                </label>
                                <span id="tone-freq-b-val" style="font-size:0.8rem; font-family:monospace; min-width:30px; text-align:right;">442 Hz</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <input type="range" id="tone-freq-b" min="50" max="1000" value="442" style="width:100%; display:block;">
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-right">
            <div class="panel card">
                <h2>Speed of Sound ‚è±Ô∏è</h2>
                <div style="text-align:center; margin:10px 0;">
                    <div style="font-size:2rem; color:#fff;" id="speed-dt">-- ms</div>
                    <div style="color:var(--success);">Est: <span id="speed-est">-- m/s</span></div>
                </div>
                <label>Distance (m): <input type="number" id="speed-distance" value="2" style="width:50px; background:#000; color:#fff; border:1px solid #444;"></label>
                <button id="btn-speed-start" class="btn primary" style="width:100%; margin-top:10px;">Arm Trigger</button>
                <div id="speed-status" style="text-align:center; margin-top:5px; color:#ffd700; font-size:0.8rem;">Idle</div>
                <hr style="border:0; border-top:1px solid #222; margin:12px 0;">
                <h3 style="margin:0 0 6px 0; font-size:0.9rem; color:#ccc;">Doppler Shift</h3>
                <label style="font-size:0.85rem; color:#aaa;">Base Freq (Hz): <input type="number" id="doppler-base" value="440" style="width:70px; background:#000; color:#fff; border:1px solid #444; margin-left:6px;"></label>
                <div style="display:flex; justify-content:space-between; margin-top:6px; font-size:0.9rem; color:#ccc;">
                    <span>Shift: <b id="doppler-shift">-- Hz</b></span>
                    <span>v‚âà <b id="doppler-speed">-- m/s</b></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="panel card">
                <h2>History üìú</h2>
                <canvas id="history-canvas"></canvas>
                <div style="margin-top:10px; color:#888; font-size:0.9rem;">
                    <div id="mic-joke-header">[Joke of the Session üê®]</div>
                    <div id="mic-joke-text">Loading...</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Spectrum Explainer Modal -->
<div id="spectrum-modal" class="modal-overlay">
    <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
            <h2 style="margin:0; color:#fff;">Spectrum Analysis & Calculus</h2>
            <button class="btn-close" id="btn-close-modal">√ó</button>
        </div>
        <canvas id="spectrum-modal-canvas"></canvas>
        <div class="modal-body">
            <h3>1. The Logarithmic Scale</h3>
            <p>Unlike a standard linear graph where grid lines are evenly spaced ($1, 2, 3...$), this graph uses a <strong>Logarithmic Scale</strong> (base 10). Notice how the distance from $100\text{Hz}$ to $200\text{Hz}$ is roughly the same as $1\text{kHz}$ to $2\text{kHz}$. This matches human hearing: we perceive pitch in <em>ratios</em> (octaves), not arithmetic differences.</p>
            
            <h3>2. The Calculus Connection: Fourier Series</h3>
            <p>This graph visualizes the fundamental theorem of signal processing, rooted in Calculus. Any complex periodic function $f(t)$ (like your voice) can be decomposed into an infinite sum of simple sine and cosine waves:</p>
            
            <div class="math-block">
                $$ f(t) = a_0 + \sum_{n=1}^{\infty} \left( a_n \cos(n\omega_0 t) + b_n \sin(n\omega_0 t) \right) $$
            </div>
            
            <p>The <strong>Fast Fourier Transform (FFT)</strong> algorithm computes these coefficients ($a_n, b_n$) in real-time. The height of each bar on this graph represents the Amplitude ($\sqrt{a_n^2 + b_n^2}$) of that specific frequency component.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="../js/mic-app.js"></script>
<script src="../arm/js/jokes.js"></script>
<script>
    window.addEventListener('load', () => {
        const jokeEl = document.getElementById('mic-joke-text');
        if (!jokeEl) return;
        const render = () => {
            if (window.mathJokes && window.mathJokes.length) {
                const j = window.mathJokes[Math.floor(Math.random() * window.mathJokes.length)];
                jokeEl.textContent = `"${j}"`;
            } else {
                setTimeout(render, 200);
            }
        };
        render();
    });
    window.addEventListener('load', () => {
        const btn = document.getElementById('btn-help');
        if (!btn) return;
        btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
            alert("Microphone Lab Guide:\n\n1) Start Mic and allow permission.\n2) Spectrum: strongest bins = loudest freqs.\n3) Pitch: locks on single tones.\n4) Scope: adjust Zoom X / Gain Y, use Pause to inspect, Copy CSV to analyze.\n5) Speed of Sound/Doppler: clap twice or enter base freq to see shift.");
        });
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>
